ARTICLE
Gut microbiota regulate insomnia-like behaviors via gut-brain
metabolic axis
Zhe Wang1,11, Zhong Wang
1,11, Tangsheng Lu2,11, Guohao Yuan
3,11, Wenhao Chen4, Jin Jin5, Xianhong Jiang6, Wei Yan
