AUTHOR CONTRIBUTIONS
LL, YH, HW, ZW, and ZhongW conceived the project and designed the experiments.
ZW, TL, and GY performed the EEG/EMG recordings, optogenetic and chemogenetic
experiments, and ﬁber photometry recordings. GZ, JJ, GY, and ZW performed the
patch-clamp recording experiments. HW and XJ provided additional support for the
GF animal experiments. ZhongW and WC performed clinical sample and data
collection. ZW, ZhongW, TL, GY, XL, and YB contributed to the data analysis. ZW and
ZhongW prepared the ﬁrst draft of the manuscript. GZ, WY, JS, KY, XL, YH, and LL
revised the manuscript. All authors read and approved the ﬁnal version of the
manuscript.
